config.name: Viewshed
config.description: Calculates the viewshed of a point given a user defined location and viewing distance.

inputParams.name: Input_Observation_Point
inputParams.description: The input location from which the viewshed should be calculated.
inputParams.label: Input_Observation_Point

inputParams.name: Viewshed_Distance
inputParams.description: The maximum distance from the input point for which the viewshed should be calculated. The maximum allowed distance is 20000 meters.
inputParams.label: Viewshed_Distance

outputParams.name: Viewshed_Result
outputParams.description: The resulting viewshed feature class given the user location and maximum distance.
outputParams.label: Viewshed_Result

inputParams.name: InputFeatures
inputParams.description: Input FeatureSet to perform analysis.  Cell size and output units will be automatically derived based on input data source.
inputParams.label: InputFeatures
